{"tid":1657132,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"陳彥霖極可能被中共特務殺害、拋屍","createTime":"2019-10-16T02:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T05:29:08.000Z","uid":253978,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9046e96b7adc5126ed8981682509b862d006bd9e","tid":1657132,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:50:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/k68bBNm5UJg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fk68bBNm5UJg&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=0de50345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/k68bBNm5UJg</a><br />\n首先，燒山認為<span style=\"color: red;\">陳彥霖只可能是自殺或被警察殺害</span>，<br />\n所以我哋已經可以<span style=\"color: red;\">排除呢2個可能性</span>。<br />\n<br />\n再跟據呢個post，<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2946314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2946314&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=a93854a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2946314&h=7932745e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2946314</a><br />\n香港反送中持續4個月，港警暴力鎮壓不斷升級，並爆出多起多起年輕人失蹤、自殺及被殺案，引發香港社會人心惶惶，而根據網友的最新爆料，指逾2萬名來自中共的公安、武警及秘密特工，已經進入香港進行「地下執法」，當中分成2股力量，一是冒充港警執行捉捕及清場；<span style=\"color: red;\">另一支來自中共國安人員組成的「祕密特工」，執行竊聽、綁架及謀殺棄屍等</span>。<br />\n<br />\n這起訊息來自署名「君子蘭」的網友在推特上爆料，他連發數文詳述暗殺力量的存在。<br />\n<br />\n據君子蘭的說法，這兩支暗藏在港警之中的力量，一支是中共廣東公安和武警，直接穿上加入港警制服，跟港警一起動作，負責在示威現場驅散、毆打、捉捕、清場任務；不同的是，這群冒充港警的公安已獲得高層授意，可以「在捉捕示威者過程中會肆無忌憚地過分使用武力」，且不會承擔任何的法律後果。<br />\n<br />\n另一支地下執法的力量，來自中共國安所屬的秘密特工，直接聽命北京國安部和廣東國安廳指揮，且可以<span style=\"color: red;\">指揮港警</span>，除了少數合作對象外，不會在港警系統上留下任何紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n這隊人馬主要負責對示威運動的核心人物進行<span style=\"color: red;\">電訊竊聽、跟蹤偵查、綁架密捕、刑訊迫供、謀殺棄屍的祕密任務</span>，目的是要查清示威活動的核心人物、示威者間的互動方式、領導機構&hellip;&hellip;..等內容，以打擊瓦解示威運動。<br />\n<br />\n為達目的，這支祕密特工甚至不惜使用包括<span style=\"color: red;\">恐嚇引誘、暴力折磨、強姦輪姦、催眠餵藥，對不合作者一概會被自殺、棄屍</span>。<br />\n<br />\n君子蘭更說，即使目前香港已經出現多起無名屍，未來可能還會有更多人「被自殺」及發現更多無名屍。<br />\n<br />\n綜合以上，陳彥霖極大機會<span style=\"color: red;\">被中共特務殺害、棄屍，並要求黑警配合毀屍滅跡</span>。所以黑警先要咁急咁火化佢<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"8d118c16467ecb8c6342c674834714dfd4d55c39","tid":1657132,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:50:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Yk6szE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Yk6szE.jpg&h=f0e63ff5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a12e50e96b8389ae7b931f44662f5eb25223d021","tid":1657132,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:51:27.000Z","msg":"死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383aae4c092c38bad717db4f0e5cbc1c84954860","tid":1657132,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:54:04.000Z","msg":"死黑警同中共特務合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9399ae26578fc6e94e1eef285ae7a1ffe8bbd0d7","tid":1657132,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:54:46.000Z","msg":"死黑警同中共特務合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ffcf8ae42e7fc09847a54dca57f4d3dc3ef2ff6","tid":1657132,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:55:59.000Z","msg":"死黑警同中共特務合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\